                </dateline>
                <p>The heading “Yugoslavia (Special Clauses)” should be replaced by “People’s
                    Federative Republic of Yugoslavia (Special Clause).”</p>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 11</hi>
                </p>
                <list>
                    <label>1.</label>
                    <item>In paragraph 1, line 3, the words “and 16” should be replaced by: “and
                        subject to the provisions of Article 16.”</item>
                    <label>2.</label>
                    <item>Add at the end of paragraph 1: <quote rend="blockquote">
                            <p>“(<hi rend="italic">c</hi>) The area bounded by lines defined as
                                follows: <list>
                                    <label>1.</label>
                                    <item>45°10'15" N.—13°2'50" E.</item>
                                    <label>2.</label>
                                    <item>44°51'10" N.—13°37' E.</item>
                                    <label>3.</label>
                                    <item>44°40' N.—13°55'40" E.</item>
                                    <label>4.</label>
                                    <item>44°56'25" N.—14°18' E.</item>
                                </list>
                            </p>
                        </quote>
                    </item>
                </list>
            </div>
